<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title/><link>https://zysongg.github.io/</link><atom:link href="https://zysongg.github.io/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><description/><generator>HugoBlox Kit (https://hugoblox.com)</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 24 Oct 2022 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><image><url>https://zysongg.github.io/media/icon_hu_da05098ef60dc2e7.png</url><title/><link>https://zysongg.github.io/</link></image><item><title>FIPRNet</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/projects/fiprnet/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/projects/fiprnet/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Combines Frequency Interpolation Decomposition with Period-aware Regularization Patching. Derives a principled closed-form cutoff frequency from anti-imaging filtering theory. Published in Knowledge-Based Systems.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>FIPRNet</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/projects/fiprnet/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/projects/fiprnet/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;结合频率插值分解与周期感知正则化补丁，从反混叠滤波理论推导出封闭形式的截止频率。发表于 Knowledge-Based Systems。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Frequency Interpolation with Period-aware Regularization for Robust Long-term Time Series Forecasting</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/publications/kbs-2026-fiprnet/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/publications/kbs-2026-fiprnet/</guid><description/></item><item><title>基于频率插值与周期感知正则化的鲁棒长期时间序列预测</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/publications/kbs-2026-fiprnet/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/publications/kbs-2026-fiprnet/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Diffusion-Based Spatio-Temporal Channel Prediction via Non-Stationarity Decoupling</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/publications/tccn-2026-dstn/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/publications/tccn-2026-dstn/</guid><description/></item><item><title>基于非平稳性解耦的扩散时空信道预测</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/publications/tccn-2026-dstn/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/publications/tccn-2026-dstn/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Channel, Trend and Periodic-Wise Representation Learning for Multivariate Long-term Time Series Forecasting</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/publications/icassp-2026-ctpnet/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/publications/icassp-2026-ctpnet/</guid><description/></item><item><title>CTPNET</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/projects/ctpnet/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/projects/ctpnet/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;A novel framework that learns representations from three complementary perspectives: inter-channel dependencies, intra-subsequence trend variations, and inter-subsequence periodic patterns. Published at ICASSP 2026.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>CTPNET</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/projects/ctpnet/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/projects/ctpnet/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;从通道间依赖、子序列内趋势变化和子序列间周期模式三个互补视角学习表征的新框架。发表于 ICASSP 2026。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>面向多变量长期时间序列预测的通道-趋势-周期表征学习</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/publications/icassp-2026-ctpnet/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/publications/icassp-2026-ctpnet/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Channel Prediction Based on Spatially Dependent Diffusion Models</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/publications/wcsp-2025-sddm/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/publications/wcsp-2025-sddm/</guid><description/></item><item><title>SDDM</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/projects/sddm/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/projects/sddm/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;A channel prediction scheme utilizing spatial dependence based on diffusion models. Extracts spatial and temporal correlations via transformers for denoising within the diffusion framework. Published at WCSP 2025 and IEEE TCCN.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>SDDM</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/projects/sddm/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/projects/sddm/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;利用基于扩散模型的空间依赖进行信道预测，通过 Transformer 在扩散框架内提取空间和时间相关性。发表于 WCSP 2025 和 IEEE TCCN。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>基于空间依赖扩散模型的信道预测</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/publications/wcsp-2025-sddm/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/publications/wcsp-2025-sddm/</guid><description/></item><item><title>TSFLib</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/projects/tsflib/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/projects/tsflib/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;A unified framework for time series forecasting research, supporting state-of-the-art models including CTPNET and FIPRNet. Features standardized benchmarking across multiple real-world datasets.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>TSFLib</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/projects/tsflib/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/projects/tsflib/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;面向时间序列预测研究的统一框架，支持 CTPNET、FIPRNet 等最新模型，并在多个真实数据集上进行标准化评测。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Experience</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/experience/</link><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/experience/</guid><description/></item><item><title>经历</title><link>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/experience/</link><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zysongg.github.io/zh/experience/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>